{"tid":306194,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過生唇瘡(爛嘴角)","createTime":"2017-07-02T10:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T05:13:27.000Z","uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a12abfb9e69c00e78cfbb46a519d9ff30d96e117","tid":306194,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:27:37.000Z","msg":"我已經睇左 2次西醫<br />\n<br />\n第一次醫生開左5% acyclovir cream (查完)<br />\n本身好番少少，幾日後發燒 ，即刻復發，仲要嚴重左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後即刻去睇番醫生 開埋hiv3 隻藥膏，查左幾日好番d，但係仲係feel到好痛<br />\n同好紅。 同埋個咀角好乾好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夜晚無論搽豬油膏/凡士林/唇膏 <br />\n第2朝都係好乾同好痛<br />\n<br />\n究竟先點做先會好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf63ff0e77eb6434a475306e7bbbab8244f38090","tid":306194,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3470ed6f2c7d018014f41ae5a934dbc77b6daacb","tid":306194,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:41:36.000Z","msg":"抵抗力差捱夜就會<br />\n食維他命b2 好似有用"},{"pid":"8118df22f7b323eafc36116a1bb5a592732bb326","tid":306194,"uid":118830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用澳洲 pawpaw"},{"pid":"c07ca1bbad6570daaaed0304f5402a3ed2331e95","tid":306194,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:43:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抵抗力差捱夜就會<br />\n食維他命b2 好似有用</blockquote><br />\n有飲 飲左幾日<br />\n<br />\n但冇乜改善 應該都會keep住飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492bf7f9ccf8b1ff7befe49d1df285d3ed0327ec","tid":306194,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":